Linked to a lustrous bale is a lush green emerald solitaire secured in a four prong setting surrounded by 14 diamonds. Crafted in 14k yellow gold, the elegant design of this classic emerald pendant draws all attention towards the magnificence of the center stone.

At the core of a scintillating floral halo is an oval blue sapphire, held in a prong setting. This oval blue sapphire ring is inspired by Princess Diana's beautiful engagement ring. It is crafted in 14ct white gold and bespeaks glamour and elegance.

Crafted in 14k white gold, this diamond solitaire ring radiates sheer sophistication. Its twist shank is partially embellished with beautiful round diamonds for added brilliance. The entwined design of this engagement ring creates a subtle silhouette of the infinity symbol.

Symbolic of the past, present and future, this three stone ring is a great way to celebrate your eternal bond. The prong set round aquamarine effortlessly entices your vision with its lustre while opulent diamonds, one on each side, shine endlessly. A twisted shank, partially embedded with diamonds, and a leaf motif carved on the gallery further uplift the charm of this two tone ring.

A round enhanced black diamond is suspended from a white diamond encrusted bar bale with intricate milgrain detailing. The sparkling white diamonds beautifully highlight the intense hue of the alluring black diamond. This black diamond solitaire pendant is exquisitely crafted in 14ct white gold.

Crafted in 23ct Yellow gold, this bridal ring set is sure to allure. The traditional ring features an oval design and self printed with natural ink. The Minimal Unisize Ring is a polished version of our best-selling Ring. Depending on your preferred finger and your size you can wear the ring with the opening hidden, visible, closed, or overlapping. This ring has both a polished exterior and interior.

This classic solitaire citrine pendant elegantly delights with its the pleasing honey-yellow hue. Gracefully suspended from a shiny metal bale, the prong set pear-shaped gem looks fascinatingly beautiful. This citrine dangle pendant is crafted in 14ct yellow gold.
